{
  "text": "In studies that examined health insurance, having no insurance or Medicaid coverage is associated with a higher proportion of LSBC [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Kuzmiak [CITATION_3] found that, compared to insured patients, uninsured patients had a 66 % higher likelihood of presenting with LSBC.",
